author: awiner
msg: The prior checkin broke some subclasses that overrode createExpressionContent(), since createExpressionContext() was now getting called within the JsonContainerConfig constructor itself.  This adds a hacky way for subclasses to delay init() until at least the subclasses constructor has fully executed.

author: dkulp
msg: Fixed a failing test because of an out-of-date cert.

author: gbrown
msg: Resolve issue PIVOT-52; propagate cause of InvocationTargetException upwards in BeanDictionary#put() if it is a RuntimeException - otherwise, wrap the cause in a RuntimeException.

author: arkurth
msg: Added "ambiguous target" to the regex used to determine if run_scp_command() was successful. It wasn't catching this.
